---
title: Speedy Caramelized Tofu Bowls on Sticky Lemongrass-Scented Rice
description: This quick and easy bowl is inspired by the bold flavours of Vietnam! Sweet and savoury sing together when tofu is caramelized with brown sugar and zesty aromatics. Get to know fragrant lemongrass at the dinner table tonight!
